OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FHampstead Heath's bathing ponds will
OL,7,Fremain "trans-inclusive" after a
OL,8,Fdecision said to show the facilities
OL,9,Fare "welcoming to all".
OL,11,FThe policy agreement means transgender
OL,12,Fwomen, whose biological sex is male,
OL,13,Fwill continue to have access to the
OL,14,Fsite's Kenwood ladies' pond.
OL,16,FHighgate men's pond will be open to
OL,17,Ftransgender men, whose biological sex
OL,18,Fis female, while the Hampstead mixed
OL,19,Fpond is "open to everyone", City of
OL,20,FLondon Corporation (CLC) confirmed.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@XO]qD@EOUqD@VO]{D@IOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
