CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FA committee decided on the issue on
OL,7,FThursday after a previous public
OL,8,Fconsultation with 38,000 respondents,
OL,9,Fin which 86% of people favoured
OL,10,Fretaining the ponds' existing trans-
OL,11,Finclusive arrangements, the
OL,12,Fcorporation said.
OL,14,FFeedback from regular pond-users
OL,15,Fsupported the same approach, the CLC
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FThe corporation said improvements have
OL,19,Falso been agreed to add more private
OL,20,Fcubicles as part of upgrades to toilet
OL,21,Fand shower facilities at the ponds.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FThe decision means the women's and
OL,7,Fmen's ponds would not be considered
OL,8,Fsingle-sex spaces under the Equality
OL,9,FAct.
OL,11,FGuidance from the Equality and Human
OL,12,FRights Commission (EHRC), published by
OL,13,Fthe Government last month, confirmed
OL,14,Fsingle-sex services must be on the
OL,15,Fbasis of biological sex.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
