CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FThe watchdog's guidance, which is
OL,7,Fbeing considered by Parliament,
OL,8,Ffollowed the Supreme Court ruled in
OL,9,FApril 2025 that the words "woman" and
OL,10,F"sex" in the Equality Act 2010 refer
OL,11,Fto a biological woman and biological
OL,12,Fsex.
OL,14,FIn March this year, the gender
OL,15,Fcritical charity Sex Matters won a
OL,16,FCourt of Appeal bid to continue a
OL,17,Flegal challenge over the bathing
OL,18,Fponds' access policy.
OL,26,@qD@[OUqD@aO]rD@AOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FThe charity has argued that allowing
OL,7,Ftrans people to use the facilities at
OL,8,Fthe ponds according to the gender with
OL,9,Fwhich they identify amounts to sex
OL,10,Fdiscrimination.
OL,12,FWhile members of the press were able
OL,13,Fto watch part of Thursday's committee
OL,14,Fsession, the final decision was taken
OL,15,Fin private.
OL,17,FDuring the public part of the session,
OL,18,Fcommittee member Steve Goodman voiced
OL,19,Fopposition to the ponds' access
OL,20,Fpolicy, calling it "unacceptable".
OL,26,@|D@TOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FHe told the committee: "My view, is if
OL,7,Fwe're going to have a ladies' pond it
OL,8,Fshould be for biological women only.
OL,10,F"We shouldn't have a situation where
OL,11,Fany biological male can go up to the
OL,12,Fgate and say 'I've decided I'm
OL,13,Fstarting a process of wanting to be a
OL,14,Ftrans woman and therefore can I swim
OL,15,Fin the ladies' pond'. That's
OL,16,Funacceptable."
OL,26,@nD@XOUrD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
