PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FKatie Stewart, CLC's executive
OL,7,Fdirector for environment, said there
OL,8,Fwill be a reliance on staff using
OL,9,F"common sense" when asked about
OL,10,Fimplementing the policy.
OL,12,FShe said: "If someone comes in and
OL,13,Fvery apparently is a man trying to use
OL,14,Fthe women's pond, we will rely on and
OL,15,Ftrust our staff's common sense.
OL,17,F"The recommendation says: Enforce with
OL,18,Fcommon sense, compassion, sensitivity
OL,19,F` they will not carry out physical
OL,20,Fassessments or ask for identification."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@NO]tD@KOUyD@AOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,FCity of London Corporation policy
OL,7,Fchairman Chris Hayward said the
OL,8,Fconsultation results had "shown people
OL,9,Fwant these ponds to remain safe,
OL,10,Frespectful and inclusive".
OL,12,FHe said: "It's clear how much these
OL,13,Fbathing ponds mean to the communities
OL,14,Fwho swim here. Many people told us how
OL,15,Fthey value them as calm, safe and
OL,16,Fwelcoming spaces with a strong sense
OL,17,Fof inclusion and belonging.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUrD@YO]tD@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,F"Although our consultation was never a
OL,7,Freferendum, the message from regular
OL,8,Fswimmers and the wider community was
OL,9,Fclear ` people want these ponds to
OL,10,Fremain safe, respectful and inclusive.
OL,12,F"Whilst the Supreme Court judgment
OL,13,Fconfirmed the legal definition of
OL,14,F'sex', it did not decide that all
OL,15,Ftrans-inclusive services must become
OL,16,Fsingle-sex services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,F"We have continued to listen and take
OL,7,Fdetailed legal advice throughout this
OL,8,Fprocess. The approach agreed today
OL,9,Fprotects the character and unique
OL,10,Fspirit of the ponds while ensuring
OL,11,Fthey remain welcoming to all."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Trans+
OL,14,FSolidarity Alliance said: "This is
OL,15,Fgreat news for the swimmers who have
OL,16,Fmade it very clear they want to remain
OL,17,Ftrans-inclusive and for trans people's
OL,18,Fparticipation in their communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]vD@[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, we will inevitably see
OL,7,Fongoing expensive litigation against
OL,8,Fthe corporation by those who wish to
OL,9,Fdrive trans people out, until this
OL,10,FGovernment clarifies the intent of our
OL,11,Fequality laws."
OL,13,FFiona McAnena, director of advocacy at
OL,14,Fsex-based rights charity Sex Matters,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Many City of London councillors
OL,16,Fseem to think UK equality law doesn't
OL,17,Fapply to the Hampstead ponds.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@OO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,F"City of London Corporation members
OL,7,Fhave today voted to unlawfully
OL,8,Fdiscriminate against and harass women
OL,9,Fusing the Ladies' Pond.
OL,11,F"The clue is in the name: female users
OL,12,Fdon't expect to encounter male people
OL,13,Fin bikinis or sometimes even naked in
OL,14,Fthe showers at the Ladies' Pond, but
OL,15,Fthat is what the City of London
OL,16,FCorporation has endorsed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780657370
OL,3,CHampstead Heath's bathing ponds to
OL,4,Cremain 'trans-inclusive'
OL,6,F"The whole policy is an unlawful mess
OL,7,Fand it's a disgrace that London
OL,8,Fcouncillors think that they can ride
OL,9,Froughshod over the law and in the
OL,10,Fprocess destroy the rights and dignity
OL,11,Fof women and girls who use the Ladies'
OL,12,FPond."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@FO]
